<p>Component testing follows, where we evaluate the thermal fuse, high-limit thermostat, cycling thermostat, and <a href="/repairs/lg-dryer-heating-element-replacement/">heating element resistance values</a>. Each component gets tested against LG's factory specifications using professional multimeters. We also examine the control board for proper temperature regulation signals.</p>
